NOTICE — Data & model weights

The MIT license above covers the SOURCE CODE in this repository only.

The training data was assembled from four open datasets on Roboflow Universe.
One source (Walailak University, "microplastic-nuga5") is licensed
CC BY-NC-SA 4.0 (non-commercial, share-alike). Because the released model
weights in `models/` were trained partly on that data, the dataset and the
trained weights are provided for RESEARCH / EDUCATIONAL, NON-COMMERCIAL use.
For commercial use, retrain excluding the non-commercial source (see
docs/DATASET_REPORT.md). Please attribute the original dataset authors.
